Simple mandelbrot demo written in Go.

Uses OpenGL + SDL for displaying. Draws mandelbrot in software.

Available actions:
 LMB - zoom in
 MMB - zoom out
 RMB - pan

It is strongly recommended to run this demo using the following GOMAXPROCS
scheme:
 - on 1 core CPU, run: GOMAXPROCS=2 ./gomandel
 - on 2 core CPU, run: GOMAXPROCS=4 ./gomandel
 - on 4 core CPU, run: GOMAXPROCS=8 ./gomandel
 - etc. (e.g. formula: GOMAXPROCS = Number of CPUs * 2)
